snippet.title: Tony Hawk Pro Skater 3 "All Goals and Golds" Speed Run in 10:04
snippet.description:
This single-segment run completes all goals on all levels and gets all 3 gold medals at the competition levels.  You could also call it the Darth Maul run because you unlock Darth Maul at the end.  
Sorry the right half of the screen is chopped off.
